cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper presents a new approach to reduce the computational load during inference in CNNs, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The approach involves modifying the architecture and training procedure of CNNs, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the implementation of the approach on mobile computing platforms, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM).
